_sText:
"de_chancellery"

This is a medium sized map that would be excellent for regular DE, dm_, fy_ or gg_ servers.

A friend of mine from Denmark wanted me to make a replica World War Two bunker map and here it is. Although the subterranean bunker layout is almost exactly the same as the real bunker, for better game play I took the liberty (pun intended) of adding more hallways, doors and vents to open up the layout from having a single choke point. This is the “last stand” bunker from Berlin, Germany.
